Description

Regular version: Simple and fast to wear, for a quick transformation without need any adhesive. This version can not be glued.

Applied Version: Soft silicone designed to be glued using the specific adhesive, to achieve greater adherence to the face and more free movements and facial expressions. This model can also be worn without glue but with a less adherence. The glue is not included. You can find the Kit materials or single products on our shop  in Fx Supplies.

Permanent Make-up: Want a beautiful and complete look without spending too much time? Choose the make-up version. Permanent eyeshadow, blush and lipstick for an even simpler and complete transformation.

Chest: full head mask with neck and part of chest, to nude skin effect with wide necklines.

Neck: full head mask, cut in the middle of the neck, to wear your body suit or your high-neck dresses.

Size Chart

  1. Head circumference: 53-58 cm | 20,86-22,83 in
  2. Neck circumference: 32-42 cm | 12,59-16,53 in
  3. Depth of the nose: 2-3 cm | 0,78-1,18 in

Please note that the measures are indicative
